to%20see%20and%20do%20in%20Poland%2C%20plus%20prices%20for%20things%20like%20food%20and%20accommodations%20were%20lower%20there%20than%20in%20other%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-places-to-go-in-europe-travel-planner-favorite-destinations-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epopular%20European%20travel%20destinations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20it's%20easier%20to%20buy%20tickets%20for%20destinations%20that%20seem%20to%20be%20less%20popular%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2284cfea12-8ecb-4638-877d-d3e978c83614%5C%22%3EWe%20loved%20turning%20traveling%20for%20the%20concert%20into%20a%20whole%20trip%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femily-in-paris-wrong-krakow-better-than-rome-european-travel-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPoland%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20on%20my%20list%20of%20places%20to%20visit%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Eras%20Tour%20is%20what%20eventually%20got%20me%20there%2C%20the%20concert%20ended%20up%20being%20just%20one%20part%20of%20an%20incredible%20trip%20full%20of%20great%20food%2C%20history%2C%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20I%20wasn't%20going%20to%20fly%20halfway%20around%20the%20world%20and%20not%20do%20some%20exploring.%20We%20ended%20up%20spending%20three%20weeks%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20can%2C%20add%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20to%20your%20trip%20so%20you%20can%20learn%20a%20little%20about%20the%20country%20you%20are%20visiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225866%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taylor%20Swift%20twirling%20her%20hair%20and%20smiling%20while%20wearing%20a%20sparkly%20bodysuit%20and%20holding%20a%20microphone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67101d1e6ac7b701e7cca2bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223911%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESeeing%20the%20Eras%20Tour%20in%20the%20US%20cost%20us%20thousands.%