%3EInsurtech%20startup%20Inshur%20has%20secured%20%2419%20million%20in%20Series%20B%20funding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20startup%20offers%20AI-enhanced%20vehicle%20insurance%20for%20clients%20like%20Uber%20and%20Amazon%20Flex.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECheck%20out%20the%2016-slide%20pitch%20deck%20used%20to%20secure%20the%20fresh%20funding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York-based%20startup%20Inshur%2C%20which%20provides%20bespoke%20insurance%20for%20workers%20in%20the%20on-demand%20economy%2C%20has%20secured%20%2419%20million%20in%20Series%20B%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20insurtech%20startup%2C%20which%20launched%20in%202018%2C%20provides%20instant%20coverage%20through%20its%20app%20%E2%80%94%20or%20via%20companies%20such%20as%20Amazon%20Flex%20%E2%80%94%20to%20delivery%20and%20ride-hailing%20drivers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20the%20startup%20says%20it%20has%20embedded%20AI%20into%20its%20offerings%20to%20speed%20up%20its%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20use%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20primarily%20as%20an%20augmented%20assistant%20rather%20than%20a%20replacement%20for%20insurance%20expertise%2C%20such%20as%20ID%20verification%2C%20fraud%20detection%20and%20assistance%20with%20claim%20triage%20and%20handling%2C%20and%20we%20embed%20insurance%20into%20the%20apps%20so%20that%20it's%20accessible%20for%20drivers%2C%26quot%3B%20Inshur's%20CEO%2C%20Dan%20Bratshpis%2C%20told%20BI.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20products%20are%20used%20by%20ride-hailing%20clients%20such%20as%20Uber%20and%20can%20be%20embedded%20into%20a%20company's%20existing%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Uber%20drivers%20can%20log%20in%20using%20their%20Uber%20credentials%20on%20the%20Inshur%20app%2C%20to%20get%20a%20quote%2C%20said%20Bratshpis.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20we're%20embedded%2C%20we%20can%20pull%20data%20from%20Uber%20and%20underwrite%20a%20fair%20and%20comprehensive%20policy%20for%20the%20on-demand%20driver%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20st