%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20September%202023%2C%20diplomatic%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20have%20worsened%2C%20largely%20triggered%20by%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20Canada.%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20publicly%20accused%20India%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%2C%20a%20claim%20which%20India%20has%20categorically%20rejected.%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20reaffirmed%20India's%20position%20during%20a%20recent%20press%20briefing%2C%20stating%20that%20despite%20multiple%20allegations%20from%20Canada%2C%20there%20remains%20%26quot%3Bno%20shred%20of%20evidence%26quot%3B%20linking%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20Nijjar's%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20our%20position%20very%20clear%20through%20various%20press%20releases.%20Since%20September%202023%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20evidence%20provided%2C%20and%20just%20last%20night%2C%20we%20issued%20another%20press%20release%20reiterating%20our%20stance%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20far%20Canada%20has%20not%20given%20any%20evidence%20to%20back%20their%20allegations.%20%C2%A0Their%20allegations%20are%20politically%20motivated.%20%C2%A0Clear%20pattern%20to%20smear%20India%20for%20reasons%20best%20known%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20rejecting%20the%20accusations%2C%20India%20recently%20withdrew%20its%20diplomats%20from%20Canada%2C%20citing%20safety%20concerns%2C%20after%20which%20Canada%20expelled%20several%20Indian%20officials%2C%20further%20straining%20the%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-pak-match-soon-cricket-comes-up-in-s-jaishankars-islamabad-visit-6809377%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BInaccurate%20Reports%26quot%3B%3A%20Centre%20On%20Cricket%20Coming%20Up%20In%20S%20Jaishankar's%20Pakistan%20Visit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20value%20our%20strong%20trade%20ties%20with%20Canada%20and%20our%20people-to-people%20links%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20large%20number%20of%20Indian%20students%20in%20Canada.%20But%20the%20current%20situation%20has%20been%20precipitated%20entirely%20by%20the%20Trudeau%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20explained%2C%20adding%20that%20Canada%20benefits%20from%20these%20relations%2C%20and%20India%20has%20shown%20restraint%20despite%20the%20provocative%20steps%20taken%20by%20Ottawa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEx-Raw%20Officer%20'No%20Longer%20Employed'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20related%20note%2C%20the%20United%20States%20Department%20of%20Justice%20(DOJ)%20today%20named%20a%20former%20Research%20and%20Analysis%20Wing%20(RAW)%20officer%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20'CC1%2C'%20in%20its%20indictment%20over%20a%20failed%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20another%20Khalistani%20terrorist%2C%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun.%20The%20United%20States%20confirmed%20that%20this%20individual%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20longer%20employed%20by%20the%20Indian%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaiswal%20today%20corroborated%20the%20US%20claim%20by%20confirming%20that%20the%20individual%20is%20no%20longer%20an%20Indian%20government%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-we-had-said-no-evidence-whatsoever-india-on-justin-trudeaus-deposition-6806506%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAs%20We%20Had%20Said%2C%20No%20Evidence%20Whatsoever%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20On%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20Deposition%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20Matthew%20Miller%2C%20during%20a%20press%20briefing%2C%20confirmed%20that%20both%20India%20and%20the%20US%20are%20conducting%20separate%20but%20coordinated%20investigations%20into%20the%20plot.%20Miller%20said%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bproductive%20meeting%26quot%3B%20had%20taken%20place%20between%20the%20Indian%20inquiry%20committee%20and%20US%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EJustin%20Trudeau's%20Admission%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20startling%20admission%20during%20a%20public%20inquiry%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Trudeau%20admitted%20that%20Canada%20had%20no%20%26quot%3Bhard%20evidentiary%20proof%26quot%3B%20to%20support%20allegations%20linking%20Indian%20government%20agents%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20during%20a%20public%20inquiry%20into%20alleged%20foreign%20interference%20in%20Canada's%20federal%20electoral%20processes%20and%20democratic%20institutions%2C%20Mr%20Trudeau%20revealed%20that%20his%20claims%20about%20India's%20involvement%20were%20based%20on%20intelligence%20rather%20than%20conclusive%20evidence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20briefed%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20was%20intelligence%20from%20Canada%2C%20and%20possibly%20from%20Five%20Eyes%20allies%20that%20made%20it%20fairly%20clear%2C%20incredibly%20clear%2C%20that%20India%20was%20involved%20in%20this...%20Agents%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20on%20Canadian%20soil%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENijjar%2C%20a%20designated%20terrorist%20by%20India's%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20in%202020%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20outside%20a%20gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20in%20June%202023.%20The%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20(RCMP)%20later%20stated%20that%20six%20Indian%20diplomats%20were%20allegedly%20part%20of%20a%20plot%20to%20murder%20Nijjar.%20The%20Canadian%20Police%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20was%20connected%20to%20Indian%20government%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trudeau%20explained%20that%20Canada%20had%20the%20option%20to%20go%20public%20with%20the%20allegations%20during%20the%20G20%20summit%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%20in%20September%202023%20but%20chose%20not%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20response%20was%2C%20well%2C%20it's%20within%20your%20security%20agencies%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Trudeau%20said%2C%20recounting%20Canada's%20exchanges%20with%20India.%20%26quot%3BAt%20that%20point%2C%20it%20was%20primarily%20intelligence%2C%20not%20hard%20evidentiary%20proof.%20So%20we%20said%2C%20let's%20work%20together%20and%20look%20into%20your%20security%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trudeau%20added%20that%20he%20confronted%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20claiming%20that%20Canada%20was%20aware%20of%20India's%20alleged%20involvement.%20According%20to%20Mr%20Trudeau%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20response%20was%20to%20express%20concern%20about%20individuals%20in%20Canada%20critical%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20requesting%20that%20they%20be%20arrested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729164300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fe1e9ifjo_trudeau-bishnoi_650x400_15_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwanted-canada-to-extradite-bishnoi-gang-members-india-on-diplomatic-row-6810487%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20backdrop%20of%20ongoing%20diplomatic%20tensions%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%2C%20India%20has%20raised%20concerns%20over%20Canada's%20handling%20of%20criminals%20linked%20to%20organised%20crime.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwanted-canada-to-extradite-bishnoi-gang-members-india-on-diplomatic-row-6810487%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meta%20fires%20employees%20who%20abused%20its%20%2425%20Grubhub%20meal%20perk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227339%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Zuckerberg%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67104421a7031864928370d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%