%20small%2C%20unique%20businesses%20that%20bring%20beauty%20to%20living%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Cramer%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20also%20means%20they%20don't%20have%20deep%20pockets.%20They%20want%20to%20keep%20paying%20employees%2C%20but%20it'll%20be%20hard.%20Some%20already%20had%20federal%20loans%20from%20the%20Covid%20period%20that%20they're%20paying%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECramer%20added%20that%20local%20business%20owners%20are%20also%20discovering%20that%20their%20insurance%20policies%20don't%20have%20very%20comprehensive%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SBA%20offers%20business%20and%20nonprofit%20owners%20low-interest%20loans%20up%20to%20%242%20million%20for%20property%20damage%20that%20isn't%20covered%20by%20insurance%20and%20economic%20losses%20due%20to%20the%20disruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SBA%20said%20it%20has%20received%20some%2037%2C000%20applications%20from%20survivors%20of%20Hurricane%20Helene%20so%20far.%20More%20than%20700%20loans%20totaling%20%2448%20million%20have%20been%20approved.%20For%20Hurricane%20Milton%2C%20the%20SBA%20has%20already%20received%20more%20than%2012%2C000%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SBA's%20funding%20lapse%20comes%20two%20weeks%20after%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffema-helene-milton-relief-funding-congress-disaster-victims-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarned%20lawmakers%20about%20the%20rapidly%20depleting%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20urged%20Congress%20to%20reconvene.%20FEMA%20has%20said%20it%20has%20enough%20money%20for%20immediate%20disaster%20relief%20efforts%20following%20Hurricanes%20Helene%20and%20Milton%2C%20but%20the%20agency%20might%20have%20to%20stop%20funding%20longer-term%20recovery%20projects%20as%20soon%20as%20January%20without%20additional%20money%20from%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouse%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson%2C%20a%20Republican%20from%20Louisiana%2C%20said%20that%20Congress%20is%20tracking%20the%20hurricane%20dama