%20of%20a%20person's%20supplement%20stack%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670fcf0a6ac7b701e7cc14ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESuppCo's%20app%20helps%20people%20create%20and%20manage%20supplement%20routines%20for%20their%20health%20goals.%3Cp%3ESuppCo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220da33132-1098-4cb7-b672-1c52ce43935e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuilding%20consumer%20trust%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMartocci%20first%20started%20taking%20supplements%20after%20GroupMe%20sold%20to%20Skype%2C%20when%20he%20was%20struggling%20with%20his%20health%20and%20weight.%20Working%20with%20a%20functional%20medicine%20doctor%2C%20getting%20regular%20lab%20work%2C%20and%20undergoing%20plenty%20of%20trial-and-error%2C%20Martocci%20began%20incorporating%20over%20a%20dozen%20supplements%20into%20his%20daily%20routine%20and%20tracking%20them%20all%20in%20a%20spreadsheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crnusa.org%2Fnewsroom%2Fthree-quarters-americans-take-dietary-supplements-most-users-agree-they-are-essential%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emajority%20of%20US%20adults%3C%2Fa%3E%20regularly%20take%20dietary%20supplements.%20But%20supplements%20aren't%20regulated%20in%20the%20US%20like%20other%20drugs%20are.%20Companies%20can%20start%20selling%20supplements%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fnews-events%2Frumor-control%2Ffacts-about-dietary-supplements%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithout%20even%20notifying%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%2C%20and%20the%20onus%20is%20on%20the%20agency%20to%20find%20and%20crack%20down%20on%20bad%20actors%20already%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20SuppCo's%20TrustScores%20come%20into%20play.%20The%20startup%20says%20it's%20collected%20data%20on%20over%20500%20popular%20supplement%20brands%2C%20reviewing%20over%20160%2C000%20products%20on%20attributes%2C%20including%20their%20total%20ingredient%20lists%20and%20consumer%20reviews.%20Martocci%20said%20the%20startup%20plans%20to%20keep%20adding%20to%20those%20analyses%2C%20including%20by%20evaluating%20ingredients%20added%20into%20certain%20products%20that%20aren't%20the%20supplements%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuppCo%20cofounder%20Michlewicz%20previously%20cofounded%20two%20supplement%20companies%2C%20WellPath%20and%20Grummies.%20His%20knowledge%20of%20the%20industry%20was%20instrumental%20in%20designing%20and%20researching%20the%20TrustScores%2C%20Martocci%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nick%20Michlewicz%2C%20cofounder%20of%20SuppCo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670fdde7a70318649282e909%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESuppCo%20is%20Nick%20Michlewicz's%20fifth%20company%2C%20according%20to%20his%20LinkedIn.%20He%20previously%20cofounded%20supplement%20startups%20WellPath%20and%20Grummies.%3Cp%3ESuppCo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMartocci%20is%20particularly%20excited%20about%20the%20community%20aspect%20of%20the%20app.%20SuppCo%20wants%20users%20to%20be%20able%20to%20share%20their%20routines%20and%20health%20data%20with%20their%20clinicians%20and%20connect%20with%20other%20consumers%20about%20what's%20worked%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20take%20vitamins%20and%20supplements%3B%20they've%20always%20done%20that.%20But%20there%20hasn't%20really%20been%20a%20way%20to%20do%20that%20with%2C%20one%2C%20a%20good%20database%20to%20track%20what%20you're%20doing%2C%20and%20then%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20ability%20share%20it%20and%20collaborate%20with%20other%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Andy%20Weissman%2C%20managing%20partner%20at%20Union%20Square%20Ventures.%20%26quot%3BThat%20way%2C%20you%20could%20probably%20solve%20a%20large%20part%20if%20not%20all%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20issues%20you're%20discussing%2C%20which%20are%2C%20is%20this%20good%3F%20Has%20anyone%20taken%20this%3F%20Is%20this%20good%20for%20me%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coming%20months%20and%20years%2C%20Martocci%20said%20SuppCo%20plans%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20comb%20through%20supplement%20research%20to%20strengthen%20the%20TrustScores%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20work%20with%20more%20experts%2C%20including%20doctors%2C%20scientists%2C%20and%20nutritionists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20the%20beta%20version%20of%20SuppCo's%20app%20is%20free%20to%20everyone.%20While%20Martocci%20wouldn't%20disclose%20the%20details%20of%20how%20he%20wants%20SuppCo%20to%20make%20money%2C%20he%20says%20his%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20%26quot%3Bco-op-like%20membership%20model%26quot%3B%20that%20rewards%20the%20app's%20users%20for%20sticking%20to%20healthy%20habits%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20clarified%20that%20SuppCo%20will%20never%20sell%20its%20users'%20data%2C%20and%20won't%20rely%20on%20ad%20revenue%20or%20notch%20partnerships%20with%20supplement%20companies.%20Martocci%20said%20he%20sees%20an%20opportunity%20to%20tap%20into%20the%20massive%20market%20with%20a%20new%20model%20that%20works%20with%20its%20customers%20rather%20than%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20there%20are%20really%20unique%20challenges%20in%20health%2C%20and%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20so%20much%20to%20deal%20with%2C%20but%20if%20anyone%20is%20prepared%20%E2%80%94%20having%20done%20what%20we%20did%20in%20music%20creation%20and%20building%20an%20incredible%20business%20there%20on%20the%20consumer%20side%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20ready.%20I'm%20up%20for%20the%20challenge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgroupme-splice-cofounder-steve-martocci-supplement-industry-suppco-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729162801000%2C%22visual%22%3A