e%20in%20our%20relationship.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221140%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cynthia%20Loya%20and%20Jorge%20Loya%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670ff8843f2165d716e209b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20husband%20gave%20me%20his%20passwords%20while%20we%20were%20dating.%3Cp%3ESamantha%20K.%20Barry%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECynthia%20Loya%2C%2028%2C%20can%20access%20her%20husband's%20phone%20and%20social%20media%20accounts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECynthia's%20husband%2C%20Jorge%20Loya%2C%2027%2C%20shared%20his%20phone%20and%20social%20media%20account%20passwords%20with%20Cynthia%20while%20they%20were%20dating.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHaving%20her%20husband's%20passwords%2C%20without%20having%20to%20ask%20for%20them%2C%20makes%20her%20feel%20safe%20and%20secure%20in%20their%20marriage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Cynthia%20Loya.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20ask%20for%20my%20husband's%20phone%20or%20social%20media%20passwords%2C%20but%20his%20willingness%20to%20offer%20them%20while%20we%20were%20dating%20has%20made%20me%20feel%20even%20safer%20in%20our%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20Jorge%20and%20I%20went%20to%20high%20school%20together.%20We%20knew%20of%20each%20other%2C%20but%20we%20never%20talked%20to%20each%20other%20or%20spent%20time%20together.%20In%202021%2C%20he%20sent%20me%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-meets-husband-facebook-group-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%20friend%3C%2Fa%3E%20request.%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20yeah%2C%20I%20know%20him%2C%20so%20I'll%20accept%20it.%26quot%3B%20After%20we%20connected%20on%20Facebook%20he%20started%20sliding%20into%20my%20DM's%20on%20Instagram%20when%20he%20knew%20I%20was%20single%2C%20and%20that's%20how%20we%20reconnected.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20hanging%20out%20that%20summer%20of%202021%2C%20we%20started%20dating%20and%20were%20inseparable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271ddb9d1-89e4-4841-b7f3-591999b7fec4%5C%22%3EHe%20gave%20me%20his%20passwords%203%20months%20into%20dating%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20three%20months%20into%20dating%2C%20he%20randomly%20texted%20me%20his%20phone%20and%20social%20media%20passwords.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20my%20password%20to%20everything.%20I%20want%20you%20to%20have%20it.%26quot%3B%20I%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20OK.%20I%20don't%20need%20your%20password.%20I%20trust%20you.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20still%20want%20you%20to%20have%20it.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20continued%20dating%20and%20then%20about%20a%20month%20later%2C%20he%20texted%20me%20the%20password%20to%20his%20social%20media%20and%20phone%20again.%20I%20knew%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20communicate%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnever-been-in-a-significant-relationship-marriage-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseriousness%20about%20our%20connection%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20never%20gave%20up%20my%20password%20at%20this%20stage.%20We%20were%20still%20just%20dating%2C%20and%20sharing%20my%20password%20felt%20like%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20were%20more%20serious%2C%20Jorge%20needed%20to%20use%20my%20phone%20for%20something%2C%20and%20since%20he%20didn't%20know%20my%20password%20yet%2C%20I%20shared%20it%20with%20him.%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20password%20I%20use%20for%20everything%20and%20if%20you%20need%20to%20use%20it%2C%20you%20can%20feel%20free.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Jorge%20and%20I%20began%20our%20relationship%2C%20we%20both%20had%20boys%20who%20happened%20to%20be%20the%20same%20age%20from%20previous%20relationships%2C%20which%20we%20were%20fine%20with.%20About%20four%20months%20into%20da