%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKlarna%20is%20assembling%20a%20team%20to%20build%20a%20stock-trading%20tool%20to%20compete%20with%20Robinhood%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20message%20seen%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKlarna%20said%20it%20was%20at%20%26quot%3Bthe%20very%20early%20stages%20of%20exploring%20this%20concept%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20might%20decide%20not%20to%20take%20it%20to%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Swedish%20buy-now%2C%20pay-later%20giant%20is%20preparing%20for%20an%20IPO%20that's%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESwedish%20fintech%20firm%20Klarna%20is%20hiring%20a%20team%20to%20build%20a%20product%20that%20would%20compete%20with%20Robinhood's%20trading%20platform%20by%20letting%20customers%20buy%20and%20sell%20stocks%20through%20its%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20internally%20advertised%20four%20roles%20to%20create%20a%20team%20to%20build%20the%20new%20product%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20Slack%20message%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20potential%20move%20into%20trading%2C%20which%20comes%20as%20Klarna%20prepares%20for%20a%20widely%20anticipated%20IPO%2C%20is%20a%20deviation%20from%20its%20core%20business%20of%20providing%20financial%20services%20for%20consumers%20to%20pay%20for%20goods%20in%20installments%2C%20known%20as%20buy-now%2C%20pay-later%20services%2C%20or%20BNPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20mission%20is%20to%20obliterate%20the%20barriers%20to%20consumer%20investing%20and%20empower%20every%20Klarna%20user%20to%20build%20their%20financial%20future%20in%20a%20single%20place%20-%20the%20Klarna%20App%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20internal%20message%20said.%20%26quot%3BThink%20Trade%20Republic%2C%20Robinhood%2C%20N26%E2%80%A6%20but%20with%20a%20Klarna-size%20upgrade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20post%2C%20written%20by%20Klarna%20director%20and%20domain%20lead%20Ludo%20Lombaard%2C%20was%20shared%20in%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Bgeneral%26quot%3B%20Slack%20channel