%20the%20seniority%20of%20four%20judges%20including%20the%20Justice%20Hansraj%20Khanna's%20and%20appointed%20Justice%20MH%20Beg%20as%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20country%20in%20January%201977.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJustice%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%20was%20promoted%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directly%20from%20his%20parent%20court%20-%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court.%C2%A0Since%201997%2C%20only%20six%20judges%20have%20been%20promoted%20from%20their%20parent%20High%20Court%20and%20appointed%20as%20judges%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0They%20include%20Justice%20Syed%20Abdul%20Nazeer%2C%20Justice%20Ranjana%20Prakash%20Desai%2C%20Justice%20Lokeshwar%20Singh%20Panta%2C%20Justice%20GP%20Mathur%2C%20Justice%20Ruma%20Pal%20and%20Justice%20SS%20Qadri.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEnrolled%20as%20an%20advocate%20with%20the%20Delhi%20Bar%20Council%20in%201983%2C%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%20initially%20practised%20in%20the%20District%20Court%20at%20Delhi's%20Tis%20Hazari%20Complex%20and%20later%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20and%20tribunals%20in%20diverse%20fields%2C%20like%20constitutional%20law%2C%20direct%20taxation%2C%20arbitration.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%C2%A0served%20a%20long%20tenure%20as%20Senior%20Standing%20Counsel%20for%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20along%20with%20practice%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20Commercial%20Law%2C%20Company%20Law%2C%20Land%20Law%2C%20Environmental%20Law%20and%20Medical%20Negligence.%C2%A0In%202004%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20as%20Standing%20Counsel%20for%20the%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%C2%A0served%20as%20an%20Additional%20Public%20Prosecutor%20and%20Amicus%20Curiae%20in%20many%20criminal%20cases%20in%20Delhi%20High%20Court.%20In%202005%2C%C2%A0Justice%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%20was%20promoted%20as%20Additional%20Judge%20of%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20and%20was%20appointed%20a%C2%A0permanent%20judge%20in%202006.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20being%20a%20judge%20of%20Delhi%20High%20Cou