3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20primary%20challenges%20faced%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362788%2Fcurious-parent-harpreet-singh-grover-indian-parenting-tips-instagram-new-mom-parents-toddlers-select-schools-growth%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20keeping%20their%20babies%20engaged%2C%20particularly%20as%20they%20begin%20to%20walk.%20It%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20important%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20entertain%20and%20educate%20children%20while%20minimising%20screen%20exposure%2C%20and%20many%20parents%20in%20parenting%20groups%20have%20a%20common%20question%3A%20%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20we%20keep%20our%20children%20screen-free%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Haripriya%2C%20a%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20had%20the%20same%20query%20when%20her%20second%20child%20was%20born%20in%202017.%20She%20searched%20for%20open-ended%20toys%20that%20would%20both%20educate%20and%20entertain.%20In%20her%20quest%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20she%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20alone%20in%20struggling%20to%20find%20suitable%20options.%20To%20provide%20her%20then%20two-year-old%20and%20three-month-old%20with%20toys%20that%20would%20help%20them%20learn%20life%20skills%2C%20she%20founded%20Extrokids%2C%20a%20business%20%E2%80%9Cdedicated%20to%20catering%20extraordinary%20kids%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20a%20business%20while%20caring%20for%20a%20three-month-old%20and%20a%20toddler%20was%20no%20easy%20feat%20for%20the%2034-year-old.%20Every%20step%20presented%20challenges%2C%20especially%20with%20naysayers%20in%20her%20family%20who%20believed%20she%20should%20focus%20solely%20on%20raising%20her%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20achieve%20her%20goal%20of%20providing%20parents%20with%20essential%20resources%20for%20their%20child%E2%80%99s%20development%2C%20she%20persevered.%20She%20found%20support%20in%