ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369597%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKaramveer%20suggests%20analysing%20the%20last%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20and%20their%20answer%20keys%20to%20improve%20marks%20in%20CSAT.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSAT%20section%20continued%20to%20haunt%20him.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20genuinely%20scared%20of%20CSAT.%20I%20needed%20to%20improve%20my%20strategy%20for%20this%20section%2C%20as%20I%20was%20performing%20well%20in%20General%20Studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20his%20mistakes%2C%20Karamveer%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20an%20engineering%20background%2C%20I%20was%20overly%20confident%20that%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360088%2Fupsc-cse-hindi-medium-aspirants-ifs-officer-vikas-singh-meena-shares-tips-study-material-current-affairs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20clear%20CSAT%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20focussing%20solely%20on%20Maths%20and%20Logical%20Reasoning.%20I%20neglected%20the%20English%20comprehension%20section%20and%20even%20avoided%20questions%20that%20seemed%20doable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20aspirant%2C%20we%20should%20not%20forget%20that%20UPSC%20tests%20your%20abilities%20in%20every%20section.%20You%20cannot%20choose%20to%20opt-out%20of%20topics%20that%20you%20are%20not%20comfortable%20with.%20In%20my%20third%20attempt%2C%20I%20set%20my%20ego%20aside%20and%20gave%20equal%20weight%20to%20all%20three%20sections.%20That%20is%20what%20UPSC%20expects%20%E2%80%94%20do%20not%20negle