0just%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20someone%20would%20spit%20on%20me%20for%20no%20apparent%20reason%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Navratri-Feature-Image-1728656568.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meet%20the%20artist%20reclaiming%20public%20spaces%20for%20women%20-%20Indu%20Antony%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Navratri-Feature-Image-1728656568.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Navratri-Feature-Image-1728656568-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Navratri-Feature-Image-1728656568-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Navratri-Feature-Image-1728656568-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Navratri-Feature-Image-1728656568-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-370025%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIndu%20Antony%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20brief%20period%2C%20Indu%20tried%20to%20rationalise%20what%20had%20happened%20to%20her.%20But%20over%20time%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20she%20had%20to%20stop%20reasoning%20with%20it%20and%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20was%20not%20okay.%20She%20had%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20came%20to%20realise%20is%20that%20I%20have%20the%20privilege%2C%20awareness%2C%20education%2C%20access%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353629%2Fsocial-work-volunteer-for-ngo-social-town-helps-changemakers-raise-money-neenu-rathin%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20knowledge%20of%20multiple%20South%20Indian%20languages%20to%20communicate%20more%20effectively%20about%20what%20happened%20to%20me.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20public%20art%20project%20to%20address%20the%20gender%20inequities%20associated%20with%20accessing%20public%20spaces%20first%20took%20root%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalled%20%3Cem%3ECecelia%E2%80%99ed%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20project%20was%20centred%20around%20Cecelia%2C%20a%20flamboyant%20single%20lady%20in%20her%2070s.%20%E2%80%9CI%20met%20Cecelia%2C%20a%20local%20celebrity%2C%20in%20her%2070s%20%5Bsometime%20around%202017-18%5D%20while%20she%20was%20cycling%20with%20a%20cape%20on.%20She%20was%20cycling%20across%20Malleshwaram%20and%20I%20saw%20her%20cape%20flying%20in%20the%20wind.%20Looking%20at%20her%2C%20I%20was%20like%20%E2%80%98Who%20is%20this%20person%20and%20I%20need%20to%20know%20her%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Indu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReclaiming%20public%20spaces%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEstablished%20in%202018%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ECecelia%E2%80%99ed%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20public%20art%20project%20that%20looks%20at%20disrupting%20normative%20notions%20of%20gender%20in%20public%20spaces%20by%20working%20with%20neighbourhood%20spaces%20marked%20%E2%80%98unsafe%E2%80%99%20for%20women%20in%20Bengaluru%20using%20the%20politics%20of%20herd%20mentality%20and%20celebrity%20culture.%20Cecelia%2C%20the%20face%20of%20the%20project%2C%20was%20presented%20as%20a%20superhero%20called%20%E2%80%98The%20Gender%20Disruptor%E2%80%99.%20The%20project%20received%20the%20Public%20Art%20Grant%20to%20realise%20it%20by%20FICA%20(Foundation%20for%20Indian%20Contemporary%20Art)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20began%20this%20project%20in%20one%20neighbourhood%20because%20we%20wanted%20to%20start%20from%20the%20ground%20up%20and%20understand%20issues%20and%20conversations%20happening%20there%2C%20and%20then%20move%20on%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20city.%20Our%20first%20intervention%20was%20in%20Ward%20No%2024%20near%20the%20HBR%20Layout.%20We%20collected%20a%20lot%20of%20information%20through%20news%2C%20and%20worked%20closely%20with%20the%20local%20police%20station%20and%20gathered%20data%20from%20them%20about%20the%20locations%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20attacks%20against%20women%20happened%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6Fm_xRlYvi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6Fm_xRlYvi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6Fm_xRlYvi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Cecilia'Ed%20(%40ceciliaed_always)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20better%20understand%20locations%20where%20women%20were%20getting%20attacked%2C%20Indu%20engaged%20in%20the%20study%20of%20feminist%20geography%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20understand%20how%20urban%20planning%20is%20patriarchal%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20if%20you%20actually%20go%20out%20into%20certain%20parts%20of%20the%20city%2C%20you%20will%20see%20a%20barber%20shop%20right%20next%20to%20a%20hardware%20shop%2C%20a%20bike%20mechanic%20shop%2C%20and%20a%20paint%20shop%20with%20a%20local%20bar%20in%20the%20vicinity.%20Given%20the%20gendered%20nature%20of%20these%20spaces%2C%20we%20observed%20that%20women%20would%20look%20to%20avoid%20them%20while%20trying%20to%20get%20to%20a%20bus%20stop.%20But%20%5Bat%20the%20same%20time%5D%20these%20were%20the%20spaces%20where%20we%20read%20reports%20of%20attacks%20happening%20against%20women%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20was%20to%20understand%20how%20herd%20mentality%20could%20be%20employed%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20not%20just%20her%20project%20but%20also%20how%20to%20make%20these%20spaces%20safer%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20happens%20in%20every%20ward%20is%20meetings%20organised%20by%20local%20units%20of%20the%20Bruhat%20Bengaluru%20Mahanagara%20Palike%20(BBMP).%20These%20are%20open%20meetings%20that%20happen%20with%20a%20local%20corporator%20present.%20We%20wanted%20local%20women%20to%20actively%20participate%20as%20citizens%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20alongside%20local%20printers%20and%20artists%2C%20Indu%20designed%20pamphlets%20that%20would%20go%20into%20the%20morning%20newspapers%20of%20local%20residents.%20The%20pamphlet%20contained%20information%20about%20the%20%3Cem%3ECecelia%E2%80%99ed%20%3C%2Fem%3Eproject%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20the%20awareness%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20create.%20They%20also%20started%20a%20local%20news%20channel%2C%20which%20played%20in%20different%20locations%20like%20the%20local%20barber%20shop%2C%20discussing%20the%20events%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20area%20with%20anecdotes%20from%20the%20women%20participating%20in%20this%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%E2%80%99s%20engagement%20was%20primarily%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F243716%2Fnarmada-relu-vasave-row-boat-anganwadi-nandurbar-tribal-maharashtra-pregnant-women-inspiring-river-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen%20from%20the%20Anganwadi%20spaces%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20able%20to%20talk%20to%20more%20grassroots%20%5Bworking%20class%5D%20women%20and%20understand%20what%20was%20going%20on%20with%20them%20and%20what%20were%20the%20issues%20they%20were%20facing.%20The%20younger%20women%20were%20scared%20of%20getting%20sexually%20attacked%2C%20and%20then%20the%20older%20women%20were%20more%20scared%20of%20getting%20robbed%20of%20their%20belongings.%20Either%20way%2C%20it%20was%20a%20huge%20burden%20to%20carry%20%5Bfor%20them%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20engage%20with%20these%20women%2C%20the%20project%20began%20organising%20workshops%20at%20the%20local%20Anganwadis%20every%20second%20Saturday%20of%20the%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPosters%20for%20these%20workshops%20were%20created%20by%20the%20women%20coming%20to%20these%20Anganwadis.%20We%20were%20trying%20to%20understand%20what%20the%20issues%20were.%20For%20example%2C%20they%20would%20talk%20about%20a%20particular%20street%20with%20absolutely%20no%20LED%20lights%20and%20whether%20we%20could%20get%20some%20street%20lights%20put%20there%20so%20it%20makes%20them%20a%20little%20more%20comfortable%20to%20walk%20on%20those%20streets%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20then%20write%20out%20a%20petition%2C%20go%20to%20the%20BBMP%20meetings%2C%20give%20it%20to%20the%20corporator%2C%20and%20then%20get%20these%20street%20lights%20actually%20put%20up%20in%20these%20unsafe%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FByZVqUJF1OX%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FByZVqUJF1OX%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FByZVqUJF1OX%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Cecilia'Ed%20(%40ceciliaed_always)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20engagements%20like%20these%2C%20Indu%20and%20her%20band%20of%20volunteers%20also%20started%20initiatives%20like%20%E2%80%98Open%20Bar%20Nights%E2%80%99%20as%20part%20of%20the%20project.%20For%20a%20woman%20in%20Bengaluru%20to%20have%20a%20drink%2C%20she%20would%20have%20to%20go%20to%20a%20club%20or%20pub%20and%20buy%20expensive%20alcohol.%20But%20these%20%E2%80%98shady%E2%80%99%20bars%20with%20grill%20bars%20on%20the%20outside%20serving%20cheap%20liquor%20were%20not%20accessible%20because%20women%20never%20f