%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FArticle-banner-1728051322-500x60.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FArticle-banner-1728051322-150x18.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368848%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2275%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mentions%20of%20menstrual%20stigma%20and%20exile%2C%20sexual%20exploitation%2C%20medical%20neglect%2C%20and%20death%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COf%20all%20the%20forms%20of%20inequality%2C%20injustice%20in%20health%20care%20is%20the%20most%20shocking%20and%20inhumane.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20Martin%20Luther%20King%2C%20Jr.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20heartlands%20of%20Maharashtra%20(Gadchiroli%20district%20to%20be%20precise)%2C%20lie%20a%20cluster%20of%20crumbling%20mud%20structures%3B%20bamboo%20and%20dread%20make%20up%20the%20scaffolding.%20The%20scanty%20roofs%20provide%20no%20respite%20from%20the%20torrential%20rain%3B%20the%20fraying%20walls%20aren%E2%80%99t%20adept%20at%20blocking%20out%20the%20chill.%20Dogs%2C%20pigs%2C%20mosquitoes%2C%20scorpions%2C%20and%20snakes%20interpret%20the%20absence%20of%20doors%20as%20an%20invitation%20to%20flit%20in%20and%20out%20as%20they%20please%3B%20meaning%20sleepless%20nights%20for%20the%20shanty%E2%80%99s%20residents%20%E2%80%94%20women%20of%20the%20Madia%20community%20who%20are%20exiled%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekurma%20ghar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(period%20hut)%20during%20%3Cem%3Epali%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267937%2Fmenstrual-health-period-poverty-delhi-pinkishe-social-impact-facebook-community%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20cycle%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20inhumanity%20spotlights%20the%20degree%20to%20which%20periods%20are%20stigmatised%20in%20some%20tribal%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%201985%2C%20when%20Dr%20Rani%20Bang%20(73)%2C%20an%20MD%20in%20obstetrics%20and%20gynaecology%20got%20wind%20of%20the%20death%20of%20an%2018-year-old%20who%20had%20succumbed%20to%20a%20snake%20bite%20while%20holed%20up%20in%20the%20kurma%20ghar%2C%20she%20was%20appalled.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20newly-married%20girl%20had%20been%20bitten%20by%20a%20cobra%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20found%20out.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20anti-venom%20was%20available%2C%20no%20one%20was%20ready%20to%20administer%20it%20to%20her%20while%20she%20was%20menstruating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20snake%20bite%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20caused%20her%20death%3B%20a%20venomous%20ethos%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20Dr%20Rani%20unearthed%20the%20regressive%20interpretations%20of%20traditions%20that%20prevailed%20in%20Gadchiroli%2C%20the%20more%20aghast%20she%20was%20left.%20Ironically%2C%20antiquated%20concepts%20like%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekurma%20ghar%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewere%20revered.%20As%20she%20learnt%2C%20the%20edgy%20living%20setup%20could%20accommodate%20three%20to%20four%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F140332%2Fpune-college-students-crowdfund-sanitary-napkins%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstruating%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20time.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20women%20were%20supposed%20to%20cook%20for%20themselves%20while%20sometimes%20their%20family%20members%20would%20bring%20them%20food.%20But%20they%20had%20to%20leave%20it%20outside%20the%20hut.%E2%80%9D%20For%20the%20entire%20duration%20of%20the%20menstrual%20exile%2C%20the%20woman%20was%20not%20to%20be%20touched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-1-1728467626.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20antiquated%20kurma%20ghar%20concept%20involves%20women%20living%20in%20a%20mud%20hut%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20their%20menstrual%20cycle%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-1-1728467626.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-1-1728467626-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-1-1728467626-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-1-1728467626-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-1-1728467626-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369358%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20antiquated%20%3Cem%3Ekurma%20ghar%3C%2Fem%3E%20concept%20involves%20women%20living%20in%20a%20mud%20hut%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20their%20menstrual%20cycle.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20hut%2C%20their%20stock%20of%20period%20cloths%20was%20bait%20for%20lizards%20and%20mice.%20And%20god%20forbid%20the%20women%20run%20out%20of%20pads%2C%20they%20were%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20nature.%20Sometimes%20%3Cem%3Emahua%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20tropical%20Indian%20tree)%20leaves%20covered%20in%20paddy%20chaff%20served%20the%20purpose%3B%20other%20times%20banana%20leaves%20helped%20soak%20the%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20really%20amused%20Dr%20Rani%20was%20the%20fervour%20with%20which%20the%20women%20regarded%20the%20system.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20told%20me%20that%20they%20liked%20the%20days%20they%20spent%20at%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekurma%20ghar%3C%2Fem%3E%20because%20it%20was%20a%20chance%20to