%20half%20times%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20underweight%20than%20children%20from%20other%20communities.%20This%20owes%20to%20malnourished%20expectant%20mothers%2C%20a%20study%20found%2C%20whose%20findings%20revealed%20that%20only%2025%20percent%20of%20pregnant%20and%20lactating%20tribal%20women%20had%20adequate%20protein%20and%20calorie%20intake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20biggest%20killer%20is%20misinformation%2C%20Dr%20Rani%20remarked%20through%20her%20years%20of%20work%20with%20women%20in%20Gadchiroli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20four%20major%20issues%20that%20I%20have%20seen%20women%20here%20face%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F143287%2Fup-menstruation-padman-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reproductive%20tract%20infections%20that%20are%20manifested%20in%20the%20form%20of%20white%20discharge%2C%20uterine%20cancers%2C%20and%20infertility%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rani%20shares.%20She%20spotlights%20the%20gaps%20and%20potential%20solutions%20that%20will%20better%20healthcare%20outcomes%20in%20tribal%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAddress%20the%20gap%20in%20knowledge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMisinformation%20is%20benign%20until%20it%E2%80%99s%20not.%20As%20Dr%20Rani%20discovered%2C%20the%20cultural%20chasms%20of%20health%20are%20deep-rooted.%20Her%20conversations%20with%20women%20in%20Gadchiroli%20revealed%20that%20many%20of%20them%20consider%20%E2%80%98heavy%20menstruation%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20that%20most%20doctors%20would%20term%20%E2%80%98dangerous%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20healthy%20physiology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Rani%20Bhang%20is%20an%20MD%20in%20obstetrics%20and%20gynaecology%20and%20specialises%20in%20women's%20health%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369365%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Rani%20Bang%20is%20an%20MD%20in%20obstetrics%20and%20gynaecology%20and%20specialises%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20health.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20their%20opinion%2C%20scanty%20or%20normal%20menstruation%20indicates%20that%20the%20blood%20is%20collecting%20in%20the%20uterus%2C%20forming%20lumps%2C%20and%20will%20eventually%20impinge%20on%20their%20vital%20organs%20and%20cause%20death.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20proper%20diagnoses%20extends%20to%20children%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20as%20well%2C%20she%20figured.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20when%20we%20started%20working%20in%20Gadchiroli%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F116337%2Fgood-news-india-averted-million-child-deaths-since-2005%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfant%20mortality%3C%2Fa%3E%20rate%20was%20121%20per%201%2C000%20(indicating%20that%20121%20out%20of%201%2C000%20children%20would%20die%20before%20reaching%20the%20first%20year%20of%20life).%20The%20number%20one%20cause%20was%20childhood%20pneumonia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20she%20along%20with%20Dr%20Abhay%20trained%20the%20village%20health%20workers%20to%20diagnose%20and%20treat%20the%20condition.%20This%20significantly%20reduced%20the%20infant%20mortality%20rate%20by%2060%20percent.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20model%20was%20accepted%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%2C%20UNICEF%20and%20all%20the%20international%20organisations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rani%20is%20evidently%20proud%3B%20the%20model%20has%20been%20adopted%20by%2016%20countries%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20did%20not%20stop%20there.%20They%20realised%20that%2060%20percent%20of%20infant%20deaths%20are%20due%20to%20sepsis.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20started%20educating%20village%20health%20workers%20%E2%80%98Aarogya%20Doot%E2%80%99%20(Health%20Messengers)%20to%20detect%20and%20treat%20neonatal%20infections.%20This%20brought%20down%20the%20infant%20mortality%20rate%20to%2020%20per%201%2C000.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEducate%20adolescents%20about%20sex%20education%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346145%2Ftermination-of-pregnancy-act-india-dr-nikhil-datar-case-legal-battle-to-raise-abortion-limit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECriminal%20abortions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr%20Rani%20highlights%2C%20are%20not%20just%20atrocities%20limited%20to%20tribal%20areas.%20Their%20grip%20extends%20to%20rural%20villages%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CSticks%20and%20local%20herbs%20are%20inserted%20inside%20the%20uterus%20causing%20contractions.%20The%20patient%20is%20forced%20to%20abort%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rani%20explains.%20Though%20resulting%20in%20the%20desired%20outcome%2C%20the%20sticks%20are%20infective%2C%20caus