ng%20to%20be%20the%20new%20centre%20of%20gravity%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20and%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20economic%20prosperity.%20By%20tapping%20into%20the%20potential%20of%20these%20households%2C%20companies%20like%20SarvaGram%20and%20Samunnati%20are%20leading%20the%20way%20and%20showcasing%20that%20impact%20and%20commercial%20returns%20can%20go%20hand-in-hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20growth%20story%20is%20set%20to%20take%20on%20a%20new%20narrative.%20Proof%20of%20this%20lies%20in%20my%20conversation%20with%20farmer%20Mrutunjay.%20While%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20opportunities%20are%20open%20to%20his%20children%2C%20he%20says%2C%20they%20are%20keen%20on%20following%20in%20his%20footsteps.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20want%20to%20grow%20up%20to%20be%20farmers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeading%20change%20from%20the%20front%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landscape%20in%20remote%20areas%20of%20India%20does%20seem%20promising.%20And%20the%20feeling%20continues%20402%20km%20away%2C%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Dreams%20are%20brimming%20at%20the%20Nisarga%20Vidyanikethana%20High%20School%2C%20as%20hundreds%20of%20kids%20who%20study%20at%20the%20school%20share%20their%20aspirations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20get%20into%20sports%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20a%2010-year-old.%20While%20another%20says%20he%20will%20join%20the%20Army.%20Hearing%20these%20innocent%20dreams%20has%20school%20head%20Nandan%20Eshwar%20beaming.%20Since%20its%20inception%2C%20the%20school%20has%20served%20as%20a%20space%20for%20budding%20talent.%20Nandan%2C%20whose%20uncle%20Channakeshava%20built%20the%20school%2C%20has%20always%20admired%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20persistence%20to%20learn%20and%20dream%20big.%20His%20uncle%2C%20he%20says%2C%20would%20be%20thrilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-me